stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR
  [*] --> Pending : Model Run emits
  Pending --> Pending : Next Model Run<br/>supersedes<br/>(material change<br/>above threshold)
  Pending --> Reviewed : Planner marks
  Pending --> Rejected : Planner rejects
  Pending --> Approved : Planner approves
  Reviewed --> Approved : Planner approves
  Reviewed --> Rejected : Planner rejects
  Approved --> Applied : Apply codeunit<br/>writes Item / SKU
  Rejected --> [*]
  Applied --> [*]
